Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Waaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pushed out into the world, we are born!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Adjust to your surroundings!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump out, and breathing from the lungs is an emergency must!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, make some music - your very first shout!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy b-day! The birth of new life!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey boy - this world is ruthless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey girl - it's a solitary warground
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A survival game with no start-overs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Beep beep! Cry all you want
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use reaching out desperately
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The rule here is that there's no getting by easy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What about my disturbance-free shelter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I still want to live snug and cozy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Panic upon realizing there's no going back, ever
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.46,0:00:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We are simply poor, helpless beings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dropped in a wilderness full of unknown creatures, ego, and ambition...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold me, mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We are born now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We have always, with tears in our eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,searched for a reason to live in this new world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Born now - we have nothing to lose
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have nothing to fear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet powerlessly, ironically, we are born!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A fanfare rises, fever & dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't a disco - it's discommunication!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to tell you, but I no hablo language!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak! Babel will come later - catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The origin of all of humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,(I am a baby. I am a baby. I'm a baby.)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how great they were
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,(Yes, yes, yes, yes. I was, once.)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Life continues on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,(Fear & fearless, a neverending cycle.)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,From the moment they awaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Misfortunes seldom come alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No voice - Where we're born...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No choice - Who we'll meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, they're not for us to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting off being a nobody
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"For a cute little baby like you..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Forced to assume an identity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"Baby, let me give you a name!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,An unstoppable rollercoaster ride driven by the forces of fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's too late to get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We are born now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We have always, with tears in our eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,been unable to stop ourselves from stepping into a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Born now - we are hurt countless times,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and betrayed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But we will never lose hope
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ironically, as if it were love, we are born!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:03:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep within the darkness, we found a light (To the light...)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever drawn to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we've crawled our way out of our comfortable world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Through a dark, narrow path (Onwards, onwards...)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All alone (Onto the next world...)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We are born now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We have always, with tears in our eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,searched for a reason to live in this new world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Born now - we have nothing to lose
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have nothing to fear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Born now! Born now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of securing our rebirth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,cast aside your fear, raise your head, and let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet powerlessly, ironically, we are born!
